{"tid":297124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關羽雲長召喚]中環有關公節","createTime":"2017-06-25T07:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T08:29:53.000Z","uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6871eed08da1b887fdc2809b1c9adf6e13ca2665","tid":297124,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"香港山西商會特別舉辦首個「關公節」，於中環遮打花園舉行，以供市民學習關公忠勇仁義的精神。大會特別在山西訂製一尊二十呎高的關公像，豎立在中環遮打花園。今日展覽結束後，關公像便會移送至元朗大棠荔枝山莊繼續擺放。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/661955/xlarge/cc2fb4eea02c1270b1c0a08fb84ed2fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F661955%2Fxlarge%2Fcc2fb4eea02c1270b1c0a08fb84ed2fb.jpg&h=2295f881&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e52bdb8a8e7d4ab4c5fe83b6e97068b54c630e64","tid":297124,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:01:02.000Z","msg":"關老二"},{"pid":"81802e7437f5ca27650af662da88e6dfbc05c36b","tid":297124,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/162951_88e30798dc0af7deb0faaae295b70e7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F162951_88e30798dc0af7deb0faaae295b70e7e.jpg&h=2c388069&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}